featured_reviews.review_id:
This place is almost perfectly run, managed, and maintained.

Every square inch was immaculate, but not reeking of chemical cleansers. The inventory was neatly arranged. And best of all, the staff were professional, helpful, and courteous. I was only in town for one night, and had to take an Uber from my hotel. The man behind the front counter answered my phone call ahead of my visit on the first ring, confirmed the arcade entry fee, recommended a good travel route, and was generally pleasant to a fault.

When I got dropped off, after a look around the shop (which seemed more than well stocked in the best toys and media), the (same?) clerk sold me a *refrigerated* bottle of Rush before admitting me to the arcade.

$20 gets you 8 hours inside their sprawling banks of booths. Most but not all had well-maintained apertures. None that I saw were short of spotless. All of their many channels had crystal clear audio and video. The booths also had sturdy locks that withstood all attempts to open them from outside.

If you plan to visit, keep in mind that the $20 entry fee does include a $5 video voucher, but after that's gone, to watch more videos, you will need cash to feed each individual booth.  Also, I don't think there is a customer restroom outside the pay-to-enter arcade area.

Close to midnight on a Sunday, the place was very busy. As a few other reviews have noted, the crowd tended to be attractive but cliquish, somber, and not overtly friendly, despite what our shared venue might otherwise suggest. Many guys just hovered in the hallways, furtively tracking other visitors or, more often, fixating on their own smart phones. Inside several booths, I saw the same thing: dudes glued to the screen in their hands, rather than to the one on the wall.

And I mean, sure...it's your $20 and your time to spend how you like, but in a space like this, perfectly optimized for sex-positive interaction, I was dismayed to see so few participants and so many spectators because the landscape doesn't get much safer, more inviting or hospitable, than this place.

So I guess my one star decrement isn't so much because of Southern Nights as it's because of their strangely aloof, dissociated patrons.

Regardless, I had a great time and will definitely return if I find myself in Atlanta again. Great job, Southern Nights. I wish you could give lessons about how to run this kind of business across the country.

Burasi neredeyse mukemmel bir sekilde isletiliyor, yonetiliyor ve bakimi yapiliyor.

Her santimetrekare tertemizdi ama kimyasal temizleyici kokusu yoktu. Envanter duzgunce duzenlenmisti. Ve hepsinden onemlisi, personel profesyonel, yardimsever ve nazikti. Sadece bir geceligine sehirdeydim ve otelimden Uber'e binmek zorunda kaldim. On tezgahin arkasindaki adam ziyaretimden once ilk calista telefonumu yanitladi, atari salonuna giris ucretini onayladi, iyi bir seyahat rotasi onerdi ve genel olarak hos bir davranis sergiledi.

Birakildigimda, dukkana soyle bir goz attiktan sonra (en iyi oyuncak ve medya urunleri fazlasiyla stoklanmis gorunuyordu), (ayni?) tezgahtar beni oyun salonuna kabul etmeden once bana *sogutulmus* bir sise Rush satti.

20 dolar, genisleyen stant siralarinda 8 saat gecirmenizi saglar. Hepsi olmasa da cogunun iyi bakimli acikliklari vardi. Gordugumlerin hicbiri kusursuz degildi. Pek cok kanalinin hepsinde kristal netliginde ses ve video vardi. Kabinlerin ayrica disaridan acilmaya yonelik tum girisimlere dayanabilecek saglam kilitleri vardi.

Ziyaret etmeyi planliyorsaniz, 20 ABD Dolari tutarindaki giris ucretine 5 ABD Dolari degerinde bir video kuponunun dahil oldugunu unutmayin; ancak bu kupon bittikten sonra, daha fazla video izlemek icin her bir standi beslemek icin nakit paraya ihtiyaciniz olacaktir. Ayrica, ucretli atari salonu alaninin disinda musteri tuvaleti oldugunu sanmiyorum.

Pazar gunu gece yarisina yakin bir yerde cok mesguldu. Diger birkac incelemede de belirtildigi gibi, ortak mekanimizin aksi yondeki onerilerine ragmen, kalabalik cekici olma egilimindeydi ancak gruplasmaci, kasvetli ve acikca arkadas canlisi degildi. Pek cok adam koridorlarda geziniyor, diger ziyaretcileri gizlice takip ediyor ya da daha sik olarak kendi akilli telefonlarina odaklaniyordu. Birkac kabinin icinde ayni seyi gordum: Adamlar duvardaki ekran yerine ellerindeki ekrana yapismislardi.

Ve demek istedigim, elbette... bu sizin 20 dolariniz ve dilediginiz gibi harcayacaginiz zamaniniz, ancak bunun gibi seks-pozitif etkilesim icin mukemmel bir sekilde optimize edilmis bir alanda, manzara nedeniyle bu kadar az katilimci ve bu kadar cok izleyici gormek beni dehsete dusurdu. Buradan daha guvenli, daha davetkar ve misafirperver olamaz.

Sanirim bir yildiz dususum Southern Nights yuzunden degil, garip bir sekilde mesafeli, ayrismis patronlari yuzunden.

Her seye ragmen harika zaman gecirdim ve kendimi tekrar Atlanta'da bulursam kesinlikle geri donecegim. Harika is cikardiniz, Guney Geceleri. Keske ulke genelinde bu tur islerin nasil yurutulecegi konusunda ders verebilseydiniz.

Here's my unbias review of One love Adult video store and arcade.

I give this store a resounding 10 stars  if reviews could go that high.

Details:
This nice shop, not to far from the Lindbergh Marta Transit station and close to the 85 exit , is a small shop compared to the other area stores southern nights an Tokyo Valentino, yet it has it's charm. From it's variety of store front products, to it's arcade room, One Love has much to offer.

But of course every review has to have pros and cons so here's a short list for you the wondering reader.

Pros:
1. Number one of all the pros that most people are looking for is the arcade entry price which is 10+tax unlimited play time or till closing, store hours very 24 hours Friday and Saturday close Sunday night at 12am. You also have the ability to come and go for an extended amount of time, no extra charge.

Speak with staff for details, this is subject to change.

But occasionally you find a black thug or two and it's so worth it from learning experience,  plus you'll also have the local latin residences so enjoy.

6. Cleanliness is a plus side since most adult arcades tend to be filthy, this place is quite clean thanks to the efforts of the staff.

7. Big waiting room, great for multi play so enjoy.

Side note: the store is growing so if you were a former customer from the last guard of the store. Take the time to visit an enjoy what the new guard has to offer.

Anywho Happy Cruising.
